## Docker Hub Plan
- Docker Hub account will be created using school email
- Public images will be pushed for evaluation
- Planned image names:

  - <dockerhub_username>/sis-project-postgres
  - <dockerhub_username>/sis-project-app

Docker Hub links will be added to README.md once images are pushed.

